23
00:03:08,719 --> 00:03:15,520
[SPEAKER_01] Znači on ovisi o geopolitici, ovisi o Fedu, ovisi o kamatnim stopama, o svemu tome.

24
00:03:15,759 --> 00:03:16,000
[SPEAKER_01] Tako da.

25
00:03:20,080 --> 00:03:27,759
