82
00:13:23,919 --> 00:13:25,600
[SPEAKER_01] Pa, recimo da.

83
00:13:26,480 --> 00:13:26,799
[SPEAKER_01] Recimo.

84
00:13:27,279 --> 00:13:32,320
[SPEAKER_01] Tako da kažem oko bitcoina ima nije toliko to sve straightforward i direktno.

85
00:13:33,039 --> 00:13:42,720
