97
00:15:19,840 --> 00:15:21,039
[SPEAKER_00] Diversifikacija, perfektna.

98
00:15:21,200 --> 00:15:22,159
[SPEAKER_01] Diversifikacija, perfektna.

99
00:15:22,480 --> 00:15:26,159
